01 June 2017The African National Congress will hold its 5th National Policy Conference at the Nasrec Expo Centre in Soweto, Gauteng, from the 30th of June to the 05th of July 2017. The National Policy Conference, held at least once in every five years, reviews ANC policy and makes recommendations on the amendments or new policies to the National Conference.Applications for the media accreditation to cover the Policy Conference will close TOMORROW FRIDAY, 02 JUNE 2017. Members of the media are reminded to apply online through the ANC website.No late applications will be entertained.Click on this link to apply: http://www.anc.org.za/forms/media-accreditation-application-formIssued by the African National CongressEnquiries Zizi Kodwa 082 330 4910 National SpokespersonKhusela Sangoni 072 854 5707 National Communications Manager